data.description: Don't miss out on this charming craftsman/A-frame that is close enough to amenities for convenience (just 12 minutes from downtown Newnan), but with peaceful surroundings on almost an acre lot! This home features wide plank hardwood floors in a spacious and open living area with exposed beam ceilings. The kitchen includes white shaker style cabinetry, granite countertops, subway tile back splash and stainless-steel appliances. Owner's suite on main with his and hers closets, a jack and jill bathroom and separate laundry nook. The open staircase with iron balusters and a custom farmhouse light fixture leads you upstairs where two additional bedrooms, bathroom and landing area provide additional living space. This home also includes a detached 2 car garage and wrap-around porch on a quiet cul-de-sac street. **HOME IS BEING SOLD AS_IS**. Please use Showing Time. All showings must be scheduled.
